REM ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
REM SETUP:
REM    Store this file in the bin directory of your cm3 installation.
REM    Place a shortcut to this file on your desktop, then modify its 
REM    properties to put "cmd /k" at the front of the command line.  Now, when
